        "subject": "LU-3929 MDT: deny LWP connection for system upgrade",
        "message": "LU-3929 MDT: deny LWP connection for system upgrade\n\nwhen upgrading Lustre from b2_1_x to newer versions (say, b2_4_x),\nthe OSTs will be upgraded firstly, then it will send LWP connection\nto old MDT, which causes the clients created for it can't be\nrecovered for LWP connection is not recoverable.\n\nChange-Id: I4924e8ebb082c831fa872ae61dd2614574820cec\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
